item.content:encoded:
Not Allowed

we do not allow our products or services to be used on
 
  • Hate – hateful symbols, negative stereotypes, comparing certain groups to animals/objects, or otherwise expressing or promoting hate based on identity.

 

  • Violence – violent acts and the suffering or humiliation of others. This includes such as weapons

 

  • Self-harm – suicide, cutting, eating disorders, and other attempts at harming oneself.

 

  • Sexual – nudity, sexual acts, sexual services, or content otherwise meant to arouse sexual excitement.

 

  • Shocking – bodily fluids, obscene gestures, or other profane subjects that may shock or disgust.
 

Copyright

The artworks illustrated and created by Hinachi Ai are owned by “Xeno Gen Projects”, but we allow our clients to use the artwork for commercial purposes that they purchased from Hinachi Ai as long as the artwork is not being sold directly.

Allowed Illustration(s)

  • As long it follows the global term of service.

Copyright

The Voice Models (P.S.A.I) that used on Phantasium Studio Silicon (The App) to generate an audio are owned by “Xeno CX” (The Developer).
 
The Audio generated from Phantasium Studio Silicon (The App) whether it’s via Text Input, Audio Input or any methods (except for voice models) to generate an audio file are owned by “Phantasium Studio”.

Usage of Phantasium Studio Musics

we allow individuals to use our audio or music on their creative video works as long it follows the specific requeirements:
 
  • It follow the global terms of services
  • Allowed platform: Youtube, Tiktok & Facebook
  • Credit is required
    • If using Music
      • Track: PSAI “PSAI Name” – “Track Name”
        • Example PSAI Luette – Wishing
      • Music Provided by Phantasium Studio
      • Watch: “Youtube link”
        • Example Watch: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vFoOaB_3uDQ
    • If using Vocal as Speaker
      • Speaker: PSAI – “PSAI Name” from Phantasium Studio
        • Example Speaker: PSAI – Luette from Phantasium Studio
    • If using Vocal as Narrator
      • Narrator: PSAI – “PSAI Name” from Phantasium Studio
        • Example Narrator: PSAI – Luette from Phantasium Studio

item.content:encoded:
Christmas 2023 Update

New Feature found that needs to re-create or re-generate the audio files I advised that if you want higher quality audio do not use it because it because it will degrade the quallity of audio.
In order Anti Synthesizer work, it needs to generate or create the audio again. This doesn't protect the old audio files that has already been distribute.

Version

Target: Phantasium Studio Silicon (P.S.S)

Version: Phantasium Studio Update 1

New

BATCH 1

  • PSAI Rail – Male PSAI
  • PSAI Fenrir – Female PSAI
  • Anti Synthesizer – 
  • Server Base Requirements – In order to save space on our machine, Phantasium Studio Silicon will download PSAI, Models, or any requirement in our server.  The users have an option to save the contents downloaded or re-download it once it needs again this will save alot of disk space since Phantasium Studio Silicon takes alot of disk space.
  • Server Base Backup – Phantasium Studio Silicon now be backup in one push of a button. Rather than having a portable copy of Phantasium Studio Silicon. Portable Copy takes long to process, and it takes a lot of disk space. This update, reduce it by saving a stable version itself on our server. Can be restored by downloading your backup from our server.
Batch 2
  • Anti Synthesizer (Partially Implemented) – This reduce the chances the voices generated or created in Phantasium Studio Silicon being cloned by 3rd party software or AI.

Bug Fixed

BATCH 1

  • PSAI Luette – Mimic Emotion Fixed

  • Server Base Requirements – In order to save space on our machine, Hinachi Ai will download diffusers, renderers, or any requirement in our server.  The users can has an option to save the contents downloaded or re-download it once it needs again this will save alot of disk space since Hinachi Ai takes alot of disk space.
  • Server Base Backup – Hinachi Ai now be backup in one push of a button. Rather than having a portable copy of Hinachi Ai. Portable Copy takes long to process and it takes alot of disk space. This update, reduce it by saving a stable version itself on our server. Can be restored by downloading your backup from our server.
  • Added Lora Support
